            Termit

    Simple terminal emulator based on vte library, extensible via lua.

    Features:
        * tabs
        * switch encodings (all available from GTK2)
        * extensible via Lua-scripts

    Configuration can be changed via $HOME/.config/termit/init.lua file (example is provided).
    
    Command-line arguments:
        * --version (-v) - prints version info
        * --init=init_file - use init_file instead of standart init.lua
        * --execute=cmd - execute command (also -e)

    Keybindings can be configured via init.lua.
    Defaults are:
        Alt-Left     -  previous tab  
        Alt-Right    -  next tab      
        Ctrl-t       -  open tab      
        Ctlr-w       -  close tab     
        Ctrl-Insert  -  copy          
        Shift-Insert -  paste         

    Lua API is described in lua_api.txt

